[section#sf.cmath.riemann.zeta
    [:en] Riemann zeta function
    [:zh_CN] 黎曼 zeta 函数
]

[%@library riemann_zeta]
[%@library riemann_zetaf]
[%@library riemann_zetal]
[:en]
[%zeta functions [$\zeta]]
[:zh_CN]
[%zeta 函数 [$\zeta]]
[codeblock:declaration]
double       riemann_zeta(double x);
float        riemann_zetaf(float x);
long double  riemann_zetal(long double x);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] These functions compute the Riemann zeta function of their respective
arguments [`x].
[:zh_CN] 这些函数计算其相应实参 [`x] 的黎曼 zeta 函数。

[para:returns]
[math]
[:en]
  \mathsf{\zeta}(x) =
  \left\{
  \begin{array}{cl}
  \displaystyle
  \sum_{k=1}^\infty k^{-x},
  & \mbox{for $x > 1$}
  \\
  \\
  \displaystyle
  \frac{1}
	{1 - 2^{1-x}}
  \sum_{k=1}^\infty (-1)^{k-1} k^{-x},
  & \mbox{for $0 \le x \le 1$}
  \\
  \\
  \displaystyle
  2^x \pi^{x-1} \sin(\frac{\pi x}{2}) \, \Gamma(1-x) \, \zeta(1-x),
  & \mbox{for $x < 0$}
  \end{array}
  \right.
\;
[:zh_CN]
  \mathsf{\zeta}(x) =
  \left\{
  \begin{array}{cl}
  \displaystyle
  \sum_{k=1}^\infty k^{-x},
  & \mbox{对于 $x > 1$}
  \\
  \\
  \displaystyle
  \frac{1}
	{1 - 2^{1-x}}
  \sum_{k=1}^\infty (-1)^{k-1} k^{-x},
  & \mbox{对于 $0 \le x \le 1$}
  \\
  \\
  \displaystyle
  2^x \pi^{x-1} \sin(\frac{\pi x}{2}) \, \Gamma(1-x) \, \zeta(1-x),
  & \mbox{对于 $x < 0$}
  \end{array}
  \right.
\;
[math:end]

[:en@~] where [$x] is [`x].
[:zh_CN@~] 其中 [$x] 为 [`x]。
[div:end]
